<br>
like i said in the post, we had overkill (35 people to be precise, our &quot;normal&quot; vindi kill is 24) and it was by no means an efficient kill. cleric mana was hurting noticably since each cleric (had 5) was CHing every 20 seconds. granted, when you get to the high end luclin game where cleric mana is infinite and everything has 800 million hp, is slowed, and hits for 1000+, sk's will shine there since they don't need to eat ripostes, which are a significant portion of a slowed mob's damage.<br>
